<span style="font-weight: 400;">Traditional western methods are widely used for treating Insomnia. Louise Hay, motivational leader and empowerment coach who has done pathbreaking work in supporting HIV/AIDS patients and their families, has said that, ‚Äú</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Illness however mild or severe is an indicator of your emotional state, caused by your thoughts and focus.‚Äù According to her, the main cause of </span><b>Insomnia is </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: Fear. Not trusting the process of life. Guilt. </span>

